Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//OP
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.57,0:00:17.55,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}僕らは未来を変える力を　夢に見てた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.37,0:00:36.14,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ノイズの中　聞こえて来た君の泣き声
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.18,0:00:47.16,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}笑っていた　僕の弱さを暴いた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.23,0:00:52.92,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}君の行く道は　君にしか分からない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.95,0:00:58.78,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}違う空　追いかけて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.85,0:01:07.50,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}僕等は未来へ向かう勇気を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.61,0:01:13.33,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}欲しがって過去に迷う
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.42,0:01:27.91,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}君が笑うほんとうの現在へ帰り付くまで
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.57,0:00:17.55,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我們夢想著  改變未來的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.37,0:00:36.14,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}雜音中  傳來你的哭泣聲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.18,0:00:47.16,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}揭開我  歡笑之下的軟弱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.23,0:00:52.92,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你的前路  只有你能決定
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.95,0:00:58.78,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}追逐著  不同的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.85,0:01:07.50,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我們渴求著前往未來的勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.61,0:01:13.33,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}卻為此在過去迷失了方向
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.42,0:01:27.91,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}直至回到你所微笑著的此時此刻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//OP
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//ED
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.61,0:22:31.14,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}金色の午後は　ママレイドティーとビスケット
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.29,0:22:37.74,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}散らかったトランプで　
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.78,0:22:46.34,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}さぁ夢の続きを占いましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.16,0:22:54.82,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}いくつのドア　開くのでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.19,0:23:02.77,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}…サガシモノ　何処ニアル？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.79,0:23:06.84,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}君だけを見てた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.95,0:23:11.00,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}君だけ追いかけて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.10,0:23:18.36,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}気づけば　私は迷子で
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.42,0:23:26.73,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}秘密の暗号　君だけに送ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.14,0:23:29.90,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}はやく見つけて　
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.99,0:23:35.55,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}「私はここだよ。」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.61,0:22:31.14,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}金色的午後  品嘗著柚子茶和餅乾
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.29,0:22:37.74,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}收起散落一地的紙牌
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.78,0:22:46.34,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}來  占卜夢境的後續吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.16,0:22:54.82,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}會打開多少扇大門呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.19,0:23:02.77,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}…尋找的東西  究竟在何處？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.79,0:23:06.84,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}只注視著你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.95,0:23:11.00,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}只追逐著你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.10,0:23:18.36,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}這才發現我迷了路
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.42,0:23:26.73,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}只向你送去  秘密的暗號
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.14,0:23:29.90,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}快點找到我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.99,0:23:35.55,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}「我在這裡哦。」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//ED
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.37,0:01:39.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧茲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.68,0:01:43.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是為了將來你能陪在艾莉絲身邊  
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.90,0:01:45.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該要知道的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.59,0:01:49.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到那時為止  她還是個人類
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.57,0:02:00.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一百年前在這裡被殺死的那時為止
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.62,0:02:06.62,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了某人的藉口
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.24,0:02:29.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉絲…死了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.36,0:02:35.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一百年前的…這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.07,0:02:38.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為人類…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.78,0:02:41.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被某個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.43,0:02:43.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.88,0:02:49.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被殺了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.51,0:03:11.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被殺了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.65,0:03:47.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧茲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.90,0:03:51.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了  奧茲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.44,0:04:17.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉動了嗎…		
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.87,0:04:21.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧茲君的刻印的時針…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.68,0:04:34.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧茲…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.88,0:04:37.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧茲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.07,0:04:44.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉絲…在叫我？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.66,0:04:55.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.82,0:05:06.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  你對我來說是特別的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.36,0:05:09.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我深陷痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.82,0:05:11.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是有人傷害我了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.89,0:05:16.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時  你要來幫我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.64,0:05:33.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.44,0:05:37.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴉的力量被抑制住了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.35,0:05:40.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,染血黑兔正在暴走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.17,0:05:43.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,控制不住它了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.99,0:05:45.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  麻煩了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.98,0:05:51.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個場景對奧茲的打擊好像太大了些
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.38,0:05:55.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思？你是說這些都是奧茲做的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.07,0:05:56.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.59,0:06:00.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能  奧茲怎麼可能做得到那種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.58,0:06:06.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,染血黑兔力量的源頭是封印在奧茲的身體裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.85,0:06:11.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是…現在的情況並不樂觀呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.02,0:06:15.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個世界如果毀滅的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.38,0:06:20.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被封在記憶中的艾莉絲和奧茲  還有你  
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.02,0:06:22.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都會消失
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.61,0:06:25.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…基爾巴特
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.35,0:06:31.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在不能因為你受了傷  而繼續讓你在這休息了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.71,0:06:39.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請阻止奧茲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.28,0:06:46.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去阻止你敬愛的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.65,0:07:03.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有這個力氣動啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.72,0:07:07.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑臉貓已經沒時間跟你耗下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.90,0:07:12.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷淡啊  再陪我玩玩嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.97,0:07:15.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑臉貓要去殺了那個金髮的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.08,0:07:19.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙現在正在破壞這個空間
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.66,0:07:20.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金髮？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.88,0:07:25.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說現在使用力量的人是奧茲君嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.60,0:07:34.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.46,0:07:39.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,染血黑兔的力量和我的瘋狂帽商一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.70,0:07:55.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…真的是奧茲他…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.91,0:08:05.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  和染血黑兔  還有鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.08,0:08:08.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑臉貓要殺光你們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.39,0:08:12.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑臉貓只是為了那孩子才在這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.20,0:08:16.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了她  殺光你們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.61,0:08:22.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明明是隻貓  說的話怎麼跟某隻陰溝老鼠一樣	
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.98,0:08:27.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴你一件事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.45,0:08:29.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.42,0:08:40.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最討厭「為了某人」這種不負責任的藉口了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.63,0:08:56.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧茲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.83,0:09:00.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧茲  你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.37,0:09:03.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧茲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.41,0:09:08.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.66,0:09:12.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快阻止染血黑兔的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.30,0:09:14.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否則你的身體就…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.04,0:09:15.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要毀掉…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.25,0:09:21.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要毀掉…  艾莉絲想要忘記的東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.92,0:09:25.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部  都由我來毀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.03,0:09:27.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼啊  奧茲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.55,0:09:33.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你聽…  能聽到聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.48,0:09:37.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉絲悲傷的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.98,0:09:39.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.16,0:09:42.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.18,0:09:49.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼讓你這麼害怕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.32,0:09:53.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.34,0:09:57.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會幫你毀掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.59,0:10:02.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓艾莉絲傷心的東西  傷害艾莉絲的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.19,0:10:05.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部毀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.82,0:10:09.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  笑一笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.42,0:10:12.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.96,0:10:18.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我重要的艾莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.35,0:10:21.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好害怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.48,0:10:24.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕自己不是人…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.95,0:10:27.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕自己和其它靈體不同…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.29,0:10:32.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕自己一無所知
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.72,0:10:35.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也害怕去瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.55,0:10:38.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論何時  我都…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.48,0:10:40.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比誰都…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.55,0:10:43.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更害怕自己這個存在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.57,0:10:46.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧茲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.27,0:10:50.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.73,0:10:54.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  就毀掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.22,0:11:00.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毀掉的話  你就沒有必要再痛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.60,0:11:05.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會幫你消除的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.62,0:11:15.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  只要消除掉就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.89,0:11:18.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會幫你消除掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.86,0:11:22.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  只要消除掉就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.58,0:11:26.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我適可而止！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.13,0:12:06.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基爾…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.84,0:12:16.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你到這裡是來做什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.17,0:12:17.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說給我聽  奧茲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.65,0:12:20.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是來救那笨兔子…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.60,0:12:23.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是來救艾莉絲的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.73,0:13:03.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然笑臉貓已經盡力了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.40,0:13:06.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可遊戲也快要進入決勝局了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.75,0:13:11.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如同我的預期  再過一會兒 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.49,0:13:15.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉絲的記憶應該就會來到我們的世界了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.67,0:13:19.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有你這個容易操縱的棋子在  真是幫了我大忙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.63,0:13:21.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帽商先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.78,0:13:31.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…真是的  好討厭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.99,0:13:34.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一使用力量馬上就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.60,0:13:39.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還是不要亂動比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.47,0:13:45.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是你也會消失的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.84,0:13:51.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是贏不了我的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.57,0:13:55.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微動動腦子就能明白的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.37,0:14:02.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的瘋狂帽商  能否定一切與阿比斯有關聯的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.15,0:14:04.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓其消失
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.68,0:14:11.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為它是為了消滅靈體而存在的靈體
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.74,0:14:15.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算那樣  笑臉貓也…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.57,0:14:17.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會逃…是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.30,0:14:22.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣也好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.11,0:14:28.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很鄭重地帶在身上的  這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.92,0:14:33.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是製造出這個空間的核心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.55,0:14:34.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.53,0:14:39.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一百年前的艾莉絲的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.13,0:14:43.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我實實在在地收下了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.15,0:15:00.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些…是我做的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.40,0:15:04.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對  不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.16,0:15:07.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想讓艾莉絲消失
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.79,0:15:09.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.49,0:15:16.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看樣子是趕上了呢  基爾巴特
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.44,0:15:19.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是千鈞一髮  艾莉絲她沒事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.32,0:15:40.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.11,0:15:47.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是因為奧茲…？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.69,0:15:49.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.06,0:16:09.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.40,0:16:17.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說不知道自己做了些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.70,0:16:21.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…我  差點就…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.79,0:16:23.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺掉艾莉絲了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.26,0:16:25.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.98,0:16:26.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.88,0:16:27.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧茲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.19,0:16:35.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我比誰都害怕自己這個存在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.17,0:16:38.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對  我沒有想過那種事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.49,0:16:41.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會對艾莉絲懷有的不安
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.70,0:16:43.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說那種過份的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.34,0:16:46.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉絲…艾莉絲…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.39,0:16:50.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我並不瞭解身為人類時的艾莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.00,0:16:54.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  現在的艾莉絲  我是瞭解的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.28,0:16:59.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧茲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.10,0:17:16.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.31,0:17:21.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然容易生氣  喜歡亂踢人  嘴巴也很壞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.22,0:17:25.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但其實…又善良  又心軟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.43,0:17:30.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要說了  我明明想就這樣睡下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.10,0:17:35.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還會時不時地犯傻  是個令人吃驚的貪吃鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.38,0:17:40.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貪吃鬼…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.31,0:17:43.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並非因為是人類  你才是艾莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.84,0:17:45.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也並非因為是靈體  你才是艾莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.77,0:17:53.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是從動作  想法  表情  這一點一滴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.77,0:18:00.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都傳達著艾莉絲就是艾莉絲這個事實
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.56,0:18:01.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.09,0:18:06.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會在一旁好好看著你的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.77,0:18:06.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.69,0:18:08.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.37,0:18:12.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉絲就是艾莉絲  這樣就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.49,0:18:15.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧茲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.25,0:18:17.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.05,0:18:24.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來得太晚了  你這沒用的僕人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.44,0:18:30.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.45,0:18:34.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟那時候的艾莉絲不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.43,0:18:37.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好地活著
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.33,0:18:40.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.95,0:18:41.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧茲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.15,0:18:43.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基爾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.42,0:19:01.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是隻不老實的貓咪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.29,0:19:04.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲～  貴安～  
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.73,0:19:07.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴安你個頭啊  都怪你事情才會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.88,0:19:10.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了知道了  之後再聽你抱怨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.05,0:19:13.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那東西難道是…笑臉貓？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.93,0:19:17.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  雖說變成這種醜態了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.31,0:19:22.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是曾經希望變成人  才會有人的形態
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.07,0:19:25.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然自己捨棄掉自己的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.74,0:19:28.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿比斯的意志真有那麼重要嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.12,0:19:32.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一定是想成為…  
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.93,0:19:37.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能將重要的人守護到底的  唯一的騎士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.46,0:19:44.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉絲…艾莉絲…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.80,0:19:49.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你傷心的東西  傷害你的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.34,0:19:52.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都由笑臉貓…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.78,0:19:59.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他準備跟我們和這個空間同歸於盡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.43,0:20:02.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快用獨角獸逃出去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.45,0:20:04.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊  獨角獸還沒回來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.15,0:20:06.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佈雷克  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.41,0:20:15.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧茲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.68,0:20:17.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉絲…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.89,0:20:20.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉絲！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.28,0:20:23.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑臉貓的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.35,0:20:26.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.12,0:20:28.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.74,0:20:40.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獨角獸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.64,0:20:47.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  基爾和佈雷克還在那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.80,0:20:50.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊  夏羅  快阻止獨角獸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.02,0:20:56.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏羅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.00,0:21:02.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧茲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.68,0:21:04.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基爾  佈雷克
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.70,0:21:09.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  不行  我還有很多事不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.81,0:21:14.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉絲的事  薩布里耶的悲劇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.14,0:21:17.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有那傢伙到底是誰…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.39,0:21:28.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想什麼都沒瞭解就這麼結束
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.28,0:21:39.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們出來到了哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.28,0:21:43.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸口…好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.33,0:21:44.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧茲？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.28,0:21:52.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧斯卡叔叔？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.86,0:21:54.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.63,0:21:58.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,染血黑兔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.88,0:23:42.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}那麼大隻的兔子能往哪藏啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.00,0:23:46.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}你果然是看到什麼了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.80,0:23:49.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}不要碰我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.51,0:23:52.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}夏羅大小姐是不是遇上什麼不測了？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.14,0:23:56.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}真會騙人呢  帽商先生……
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.60,0:24:00.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}他將再次給這片大地帶來災厄！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.23,0:24:04.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}將薩布里耶的悲劇帶來這片大地！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.73,0:24:09.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回  英雄與少年